<tr>
<td class="noprint" colspan="2" style="text-align:center">

<div style="float: right;"><a href="/wiki/2004%E2%80%9305_UEFA_Cup" title="2004–05 UEFA Cup">2004–05</a> →</div>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>The <b>2003–04 <a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/UEFA_Cup" title="UEFA Cup">UEFA Cup</a></b> was won by <a href="/wiki/Valencia_CF" title="Valencia CF">Valencia</a> in the final against <a href="/wiki/Olympique_de_Marseille" title="Olympique de Marseille">Marseille</a>. It wrapped up a league and UEFA Cup double for Valencia.</p>
<p></p>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent"><span class="summary" style="display: none;"><a href="/wiki/FC_Haka" title="FC Haka">Haka</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Finland" title="Finland"><img alt="Finland" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="1100" data-file-width="1800" height="14" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/23px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/35px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/46px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> v <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Croatia" title="Croatia"><img alt="Croatia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="1200" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/23px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/35px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/46px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/HNK_Hajduk_Split" title="HNK Hajduk Split">Hajduk Split</a></span>
<table cellspacing="0" class="collapsible collapsed" style="border-top:1px solid #999999; border-bottom:1px solid #999999; margin-bottom: -1px; width: 100%; background-color:transparent">
<tr>
<td style="vertical-align:top" width="19%"><span style="white-space:nowrap;float:right;margin-left:.5em">12 August 2003<span style="display:none"> (<span class="bday dtstart published updated">2003-08-12</span>)</span></span></td>
<td class="vcard attendee" style="text-align:right;vertical-align:top" width="23%"><b><span class="fn org"><a href="/wiki/FC_Haka" title="FC Haka">Haka</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Finland" title="Finland"><img alt="Finland" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="1100" data-file-width="1800" height="14" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/23px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/35px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bc/Flag_of_Finland.svg/46px-Flag_of_Finland.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span></span></b></td>
<td style="text-align:center;vertical-align:top" width="12%"><span style="white-space:nowrap; display:inline;"><b>2–1</b></span></td>
<td class="vcard attendee" style="vertical-align:top" width="23%"><b><span class="fn org"><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Croatia" title="Croatia"><img alt="Croatia" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="600" data-file-width="1200" height="12" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/23px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/35px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1b/Flag_of_Croatia.svg/46px-Flag_of_Croatia.svg.png 2x" width="23"/></a></span> <a href="/wiki/HNK_Hajduk_Split" title="HNK Hajduk Split">Hajduk Split</a></span></b></td>
<th style="text-align:left;vertical-align:top;font-weight:normal" width="23%"><span class="location" style="font-size:85%;"><a href="/wiki/Tehtaan_kentt%C3%A4" title="Tehtaan kenttä">Tehtaan kenttä</a>, <a href="/wiki/Valkeakoski" title="Valkeakoski">Valkeakoski</a></span></th>
</tr>
<tr style="font-size:85%">
<td style="vertical-align:top;text-align:right;">17:05 CET</td>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Third_round">Third round</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Third round">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<table class="wikitable" style="text-align:center">
<tr>
<th style="text-align:right; width:250px">Team 1</th>
<th style="width:80px"><a class="mw-redirect" href="/wiki/Aggregate_score" title="Aggregate score"><abbr title="Aggregate score">Agg.</abbr></a></th>
<th style="text-align:left; width:250px">Team 2</th>
<th style="width:80px">1st leg</th>
<th style="width:80px">2nd leg</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align: right;"><a href="/wiki/Br%C3%B8ndby_IF" title="Brøndby IF">Brøndby</a> <span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/Denmark" title="Denmark"><img alt="Denmark" class="thumbborder" data-file-height="280" data-file-width="370" height="15" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9c/Flag_of_Denmark.svg/20px-Flag_of_Denmark.svg.png" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9c/Flag_of_Denmark.svg/31px-Flag_of_Denmark.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9c/Flag_of_Denmark.svg/40px-Flag_of_Denmark.svg.png 2x" width="20"/></a></span></td>
<td style="text-align: center;">1–3</td>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_4">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="First_leg_6">First leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: First leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>

<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Second_leg_5">Second leg</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=17" title="Edit section: Second leg">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">

</div>
<p><i>Valencia won 4–2 on aggregate.</i></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Semi-finals">Semi-finals</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=18" title="Edit section: Semi-finals">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<p>The first legs were played on 22 April, and the second legs were played on 6 May 2004.</p>

<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="Final">Final</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=2003%E2%80%9304_UEFA_Cup&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Final">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<div class="hatnote" role="note">Main article: <a href="/wiki/2004_UEFA_Cup_Final" title="2004 UEFA Cup Final">2004 UEFA Cup Final</a></div>
<div class="vevent" style="width: 100%; background-color: transparent; clear:both">
